data.text1: Your team checks with MTF and finds the workers are not experiencing symptoms.
data.text2: The MTF representative at the EOC has concluded, based on the symptoms displayed by exposed personnel, the actual concentration to which they were exposed is most likely less than the concentration measured by the response team.
data.text3: You conclude there is an airborne hazard at a close distance to the box (approximately 2-3 feet). The liquid presents a contact hazard and could be lethal.
